content.rendered:
Energy acupuncture needles are high-quality precision needles that come at a low cost.
These are 100% sterile needles, with each needle individually packaged with a guide tube. Features a traditional metal handle.
Features:
  • Sterile
  • With Guide Tube only
  • Traditional metal handle
Energy acupuncture needles are a TGA registered device.
